title: STUNNING, HUGE, BRIGHT - TOP FLOOR - 3BR/GARAGE
posting_body: ['STUNNING, HUGE, BRIGHT - TOP FLOOR - 3BR/GARAGE - AVAILABLE AUG 15!!!!!', 'This gorgeous unit is in midst of complete renovation...ready to view when you are!!!', ' Huge & Bright 3 bedroom unit in heart of fabulous Ukrainian Village.', ' Unit faces south and is on top floor - providing crazy natural light.', ' Three bedrooms are good size.', ' Kitchen is huge with enough room for a table & chairs...all appliances are stainless steel.', ' Central air/Central heat!', ' Lovely north facing deck for that charished cup of coffee in the morning and the glass of wine at end of day.', ' Garden is also provided for tenant use but is shared.', ' Garage space for one car is included in price of rent.', ' Center of town...easy commute anywhere in the city.', ' Delicious entertaing and shopping literally steps away.', 'Can show at any time even when in time of renovation...use your imagination!', 'Sorry, only dogs under 25 lbs.', 'A pretty decent landlord.']
